{"tid":1437290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團體發起「全民撐警日」，前往中區、觀塘和葵涌警署慰問","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T14:28:00.000Z","uid":78947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ab7518b2c7244b2983c0eedc11d519469b3d35","tid":1437290,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"守護香港大聯盟將發起多項活動，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">包括明日發起「全民撐警日」，前往中區、觀塘和葵涌警署慰問，並呼籲支持的市民向警員豎起姆指支持，並撰寫慰問說話。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因應有人在尖沙咀毀壞國旗，大聯盟召集人黃英豪表示，訂製12000面國旗準備分發給其他團體，希望市民在合適場合懸掛國旗，並和國旗合照上載到社交媒體。<br />\n<br />\n全國政協常委唐英年表示，對過去兩個月的發展愈來愈感憂慮，認為近日行動升級、暴力化，違反和平理性非暴力的核心價值，繼續下去會摧毀香港法治基礎、繁榮穩定基石，當前要止暴制亂，又譴責不尊重「一國兩制」的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473648-20190809.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473648-20190809.htm&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=ad371e5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473648-20190809.htm&h=913497e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473648-20190809.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n各位點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82207795838ad1f64cec112996d410f92c72a5b7","tid":1437290,"uid":266592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"有無巴打諗過拎住國旗尼遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0991f96ccc7bdf1667ca0d7da6a68a575901a75f","tid":1437290,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"國旗呀~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i